<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.1.3">
<l>kolaiyāṉaik kompupaṟit tukkūṭa larcēṉaipo rutaḻiya</l>
<l>cilaiyāl marāmarameyta tēvaṉaic cikkeṉanā ṭutirēl</l>
<l>talaiyāl kurakkiṉamtāṅ kicceṉṟu taṭavaraikoṇ ṭaṭaippa</l>
<l>valaiyār kaṭaṟkaraivīṟ ṟiruntāṉai yaṅkuttaik kaṇṭāruḷar.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you tenaciously seek the deity</l>
<l rend="indent">who plucked out the tusk of the murderous elephant,</l>
<l rend="indent">engaged in battle so that the enemy army was ruined,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] shot arrows with [his] bow at the fig tree,</l>
<l>there are those who have seen the place where he sits</l>
<l rend="indent">in splendour on the seashore spread over with waves</l>
<l>[while] monkey troops come, bearing upon [their] heads</l>
<l rend="indent">huge mountains to obstruct [the sea].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
